{"tid":2019309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學校長會主席：教育局要求取消試題弊多於利","createTime":"2020-05-16T07:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T08:09:43.000Z","uid":55597,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"808c66702ab7a575c6c37691f42cefeb5a42442d","tid":2019309,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T07:46:12.000Z","msg":"中學文憑試歷史科試題惹爭議，教育局罕有要求考評局取消有關試題。中學校長會主席鄧振強認為教育局的做法是弊多於利，關注事件會否為學術自由及專業互信帶來衝擊，又質疑政治凌駕教育專業。他擔心事件是否意味有些歷史論述、甚至「紅線」是不能觸碰，同時擔憂教育局會否向學校實行「微觀管理」。<br />\n<br />\n鄧振強亦指，有校長及老師向校長會表達擔憂，說感到壓力，他稍後會約見教育局局長。他又擔心事件會否影響有志的年輕人入行，因為教師這個職業令人感覺不是很安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526453-20200515.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526453-20200515.htm&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bdkum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=90147cd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526453-20200515.htm&h=9b90dcfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526453-20200515.htm</a>"},{"pid":"880697ddd6bc46bb0772341f34dfaef680f1c22c","tid":2019309,"uid":69125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T07:47:20.000Z","msg":"教育局又要開記者會批鬥佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dfd3651e1f2d2b0c8cc82a938e24fcb8ea43dd","tid":2019309,"uid":276592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T07:48:47.000Z","msg":"呢D係真正既教育家<br />\n保護學生、保護教師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3024579f31df335ea004b0533ac04c59059908","tid":2019309,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3dfd3651e1f2d2b0c8cc82a938e24fcb8ea43dd","tid":2019309,"uid":276592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2